divs: Sighting DetailsWas setting here drinking coffee and heard the noise. Having seen 3 black triangulars years ago, I went out on the deck to investigate. Sure enough, two black triangulars, flying northeast over my property; pretty high in the sky. They were moving slowly; and not flying fast at all. Their propulsion sounded like a rumble, and they had flashing lights on each corner of them. I never have a camera when these things happen, but that makes 5 black triangulars I have seen in the past 10 years.
Summary: Two Black Triangulars, Flying in Formation
